IMPORTANT NETWORK USE REQUIREMENT:

If you run a modified version of this software as a network service (including
as a WiFi hotspot billing system, web service, or API), you MUST make the
complete source code of your modified version available to users interacting
with it remotely through a computer network.

This includes:
- All modifications to Lambda functions
- Custom payment integrations
- Gateway configurations
- Database schema changes
- Frontend modifications
- Any additional features or improvements

